            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Vercaius Itt<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>es</abbr></expan> <note>sic</note> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>et Agisiae Vindili <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iliae</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>et Quarto filio an<lb break="no" n="4"/>norum XXV et Mosica <lb n="5"/>Ituni <expan><abbr>vv</abbr><ex>ivi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ecerunt</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ibi</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>oc</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>onumentum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>eredem</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>on</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>equetur</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> et Vero </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> XV
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Z. 7/8: nachträglich in der linken unteren Ecke des Inschriftfeldes (Z. 7) bzw. des Rahmens (Z. 8) hinzugefügt. Z. 5: Fuchs - Ubl, AE 1984, ILLPRON, Kremer: u(xor) v(ivi). (B): AE 1984: Z. 7/8: Vero ann.</p>
